<item>
            <title>[SPARK-48045] Pandas API groupby with multi-agg-relabel ignores as_index=False</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-48045</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A Pandas API DataFrame groupby with as_index=False and a multilevel relabeling, such as&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
from pyspark &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; pandas as ps
ps.DataFrame({&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;: [0, 0], &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;b&quot;&lt;/span&gt;: [0, 1]}).groupby(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, as_index=False).agg(b_max=(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;b&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;max&quot;&lt;/span&gt;))&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;fails to include group keys in the resulting DataFrame. This diverges from expected behavior as well as from the behavior of native Pandas, e.g.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;actual&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&#160;&#160; b_max
0&#160; &#160; &#160; 1 &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;expected&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&#160;&#160; a&#160; b_max
0&#160; 0&#160; &#160; &#160; 1 &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A possible fix is to prepend groupby key columns to &lt;tt&gt;&lt;b&gt;order&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;&lt;b&gt;columns&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/tt&gt; before filtering here:&#160; &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/master/python/pyspark/pandas/groupby.py#L327-L328&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/blob/master/python/pyspark/pandas/groupby.py#L327-L328&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Python 3.11, PySpark 3.5.1, Pandas=2.2.2&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
